en_182681_0	One person was killed and five others injured in a road accident which took place on the Weligama-Akuressa main road in the Bodagala area.
en_182681_1	The accident occurred when a sand tipper collided head-on with a three-wheeler last afternoon (Feb. 01).
en_182681_2	Six persons who were travelling in the three-wheeler were admitted to Walana District Hospital.
en_182681_3	The driver succumbed to his injuries at the hospital, the police said.
en_182681_4	Photos - Mahesh - Weligama
